Requirements
------------

1. python
2. python-argparse
3. python-protobuf

Typical installation steps on Debian
------------------------------------
1. apt-get install python-protobuf python-argparse
2. dpkg -i python-hsn2-proto_*.deb
3. dpkg -i hsn2-console_*.deb

Usage
-----
1. edit /etc/hsn2/console.conf file (point to correct framework host/port)
   or use -c option with own config file
2. use 'hc' command (installed in /opt/hsn2/console/)
   $hc --help
